  "about": {
    "title": "Planyzer",
    "tagline": "Plan your events, together.",
    "description": "A dinner, a weekend away, a trip with friends… and suddenly you're juggling Splitwise, a WhatsApp group, two Google Docs and three carpool apps. Planyzer brings it all under one roof: create the event, invite your people, add the tools you actually need. One app, zero chaos.",
