    "feature1Body": "One page per outing, with its dates and participants.",
    "feature2Title": "Modular tools",
    "feature2Body": "Add whatever you need along the way: money, notes, carpool.",
    "feature3Title": "Controlled sharing",
    "feature3Body": "Some tools visible to everyone, others reserved for a subgroup.",
    "toolsSection": "The tools",
